{"title": "Practice Access : Providing access to other practices", "body": "This article will demonstrate how to grant access to other Practices.\n1. Select More from the top of your MediRecords screen, followed by Settings\n2. Select Subscription Details:\n3. Select Users:\n4. Select a User that requires access to the practice by selecting the tick-box to the left of their name, followed by Edit User:\n5. From the list provided on the left, select Subscription, then mark each tick-box next to the Practice Name the user needs access to, followed by Save:\n  Once you save it, you have now access to other practices that you've selected.\nClick here to view Practice Access: Setting practice Default\n   "}